                            <h3 class="card-title">
                                <a href="#">The Essence of a Healthy Soul</a>
                            </h3>
                            <h5>$9.99</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">The Essence of a Healthy Soul is the fourth studio album by Ken Freeman released in 2016. The title The Essence of a Healthy Soul can be seen as referring to Ken’s new-found sobriety, following the years of drug and alcohol use that eventually led Ken into rehabilitation.</p>
