                                <a href="#">Iragberi</a>
                            </h4>
                            <h3 class="card-title">
                                <a href="#">Take It From Us</a>
                            </h3>
                            <h5>$14.99</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">The Take It From Us is the second studio album by the American rock band Iragberi. Produced by Gil Orten, it was released through Big Guy Records and the group's own Open Records on May 20, 2017.</p>
