                                <a href="#">Courtesy</a>
                            </h3>
                            <h5>$7.99</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Courtesy is the third album by Canadian singer James Flint, released in 2015 through Enemy Records. It was James’ first album released outside Canada. Flint began work on his album after moving from her hometown, Ottawa, to Toronto.</p>
